<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.9.3">
<l>pēcu kiṉṟa tituvē vaiya mīra ṭiyālaḷanta</l>
<l>mūci vaṇṭu muraluṅ kaṇṇi muṭiyī rumaikkāṇum</l>
<l>ācai yeṉṉuṅ kaṭalil vīḻntiṅ kayarntō mayalārum</l>
<l>ēcu kiṉṟa tituvē kāṇu minta ḷūrīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What [I] am saying is just this: You with a garland crown,</l>
<l>Where swarming bees hum, who measured the world in two steps,</l>
<l>Sinking in the sea named ‘desire of seeing you,’ we faltered here.</l>
<l>See, what others are scorning is just this, you of Intaḷūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
